displayChart.description: Your weekly update of the most popular tracks in Chandigarh, India.

labels.name: Sony Music Entertainment India Pvt. Ltd.

highlights.text: Sidhu Moose Wala has the most spots on Top Songs Chandigarh. “Never Fold” is the highest at #12.
“Taur” by Lopon Sidhu is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Chandigarh, up 57 spots at #37.
“Excuses” by AP Dhillon, Gurinder Gill, and Intense has been on Top Songs Chandigarh the longest, at 60 weeks straight.
“Her” by Shubh is the highest new entry on Top Songs Chandigarh at #5.
